    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "Lmdsn+2D5X4WRo0vfPu1qsp4BYFBwgjfAcAvkWxZ5iU=",
    "originContent": "Both `.svg` and `.ico` files are provided. You only need the contents of the [ico folder](ico/) ([icns folder](icns/) for MacOS users) if you want to use the icons in your file explorer.",
    "translatedContent": "同时提供 `.svg` 和 `.ico` 文件。如果您只想在文件资源管理器中使用这些图标，只需使用 [ico 文件夹](ico/)（MacOS 用户请使用 [icns 文件夹](icns/)）中的内容。"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
