  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "IguK2gq4QCWV3P8CfyvQwNQCol6hnRetbKR01vAxPSA=",
    "originContent": "This rather silly project was inspired by [davidvkimball's icons](https://www.deviantart.com/davidvkimball/art/885700560) and the [Folder11](https://github.com/icon11-community/Folder11) collection.",
    "translatedContent": "这个略显搞笑的项目灵感来自于 [davidvkimball 的图标](https://www.deviantart.com/davidvkimball/art/885700560) 和 [Folder11](https://github.com/icon11-community/Folder11) 收藏。"
  },
  {
