  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "6hGVUjoew+zCd6OSa2ebB2dApgVicFUEek+F1UpRcfw=",
    "originContent": "## Cool! How do I install them?",
    "translatedContent": "## 很酷！我该如何安装它们？"
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "ktLAwMlAkdXLbjdvSXPdr+nS26lFEHBxtRpQ8phxgvE=",
    "originContent": "On Windows, it goes something like this:",
    "translatedContent": "在 Windows 上，步骤大致如下："
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "1. 克隆仓库或下载为zip压缩包（页面顶部大而醒目的绿色“Code”按钮 > Download ZIP）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "VkNEOkhHaGYJ4kldIiLCirta+JxW+7O3R3OEGSB+YXU=",
    "originContent": "1. Clone the repository or download it as a zip archive (big bright green \"Code\" button at the top of the page > Download ZIP)",
    "translatedContent": "2. 将 `ico` 文件夹解压到安全位置，例如你的主目录或桌面。记住此位置！  "
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "peb+FYBivfsKIg04+0M5rY4EF3WAJaO73rs8cgQdsg4=",
    "originContent": "2. Extract the `ico` folder somewhere safe, for example your home or your desktop. Remember this location! ",
    "translatedContent": "3. 右键点击你想要自定义的文件夹  "
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "a2/o+8fkOT/4whgti79Iku02gRcuPUDfxqV/J16sQWc=",
    "originContent": "3. Right click on a folder you want to customize",
    "translatedContent": "4. 属性 > 自定义 > 更改图标 > 浏览 > 从上述位置选择一个 .ico 文件  "
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "1gGJibX/y4b6bpL5YGrpwalljyuC0rCObe72oon+nzY=",
    "originContent": "4. Properties > Customize > Change Icon > Browse > Select an .ico file from the aforementioned location",
    "translatedContent": "5. 完成，你应该能看到文件夹图标已经更改！  "
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "E3N/sWW3RWF8UQDlVDugwffkh08MuTZFwrbNNKQjykw=",
    "originContent": "5. Done, you should see the folder icon changed!",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 制作你自己的图标！  "
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "c9dJbA47LHlyDR+pfgcATIgB8+h0B9F7FQap6oQ5OBY=",
    "originContent": "## Make your own icons!",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "这里还有一个像素完美的[空白文件夹模板](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dalps/minecraft11/main/template.svg)，是我拼凑的图标基础。欢迎随意使用，也欢迎贡献 🙂"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "ruHK6NPbckdiouS630yPpouP+fFruhrUpbdchDdFo78=",
    "originContent": "There's also a pixel-perfect [blank folder template](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dalps/minecraft11/main/template.svg) I cobbled together as a base for the icons. Feel free to use it, contributions are also welcome 🙂",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
